e, or a higher level Splurt equivalent.</P><P>Saminga Daemonregina, 58th (yes, just dinged) Bad Girl of Rodcet Nife.</P><P>Good girls go to Heaven, bad girls FD and /q out.<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
